item.title: Brooklyn Nets Subtly Update Logos, Introduce New Secondary Mark For 2024-25 Season
item.description: The Brooklyn Nets have made several changes to their logo set for the 2024-25 season, including introducing a new secondary logo that depicts a stylized net.
